# 🚀 AI Exam Center Platform

An AI-powered exam platform where users can code in multiple languages, share video responses, and receive AI-based evaluations — built for secure and interactive online assessments.

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-active-brightgreen)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue)
![Contributions](https://img.shields.io/badge/contributions-welcome-orange)

---

## 📌 Features

- 👨‍💻 Multi-language code typing
- 🎥 Video response recording and upload
- 🤖 AI-based answer rating system
- 🛡️ Secure browser environment
- 📊 Real-time feedback and analytics

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React.js, Tailwind CSS
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
- **Database:** MongoDB
- **AI Engine:** Python (NLP & Scoring Models)

---

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ai-exam-center.git

# Install dependencies
cd ai-exam-center
npm install

# Start the server
npm start
